data.text:
Delighted to share I will be performing in “The Secret Show”! Join us for this staged reading at The Shakespeare Villa in Pasadena this Thursday, June 20 at 7 pm. It’s a thrilling evening for both audience and actors, as nobody knows what show we will perform until showtime! Directed by Richard Kenyon. soulinbliss.com #actor #actorslife #secretshow #losangeles #shakespeare #stagedreading

Here’s a clip of me as busybody “Aunt Beth” in the California Institute for the Arts thesis film “Her Best” directed by Katerina Kiagia. #actor #shortfilm #losangeles #actorslife #comedy #darkcomedy

Happy Mother’s Day to my dear Mom, and to all moms! 💕 My 90 year old Mom had never been in a convertible, so when the opportunity arose, my husband Richard made a “joy ride” in one happen! And thank you Richard for the lovely flowers! ❤️ #loveyoumom #momsfirstconvertibleride #mothersday2024

On the red carpet at LA WEBFEST. So grateful to be nominated for Best Performance and Best Director for my short comedy film “Janet”! 🎬💕 Thank you LA WEBFEST! 15th Annual LA WEBFEST 2024 #actor #actress #actorslife #sketchcomedy #writer #losangeles #hollywood #comedy

Thank you for all the birthday love and thoughtful messages! 🎂🤗💕 What is life if we can’t just stop and frolic in the roses every now and then? 😉 Photographer: Dana Patrick #itsmybirthday #birthdaygirl #happybirthday

Check out my interview with eBOSS Canada “10 QUESTIONS WITH ACTOR CAROLYN BRIDGET KENNEDY” Carolyn Bridget Kennedy is an award-winning actor (SAG-AFTRA, ACTRA) and filmmaker. Carolyn appears in the 4th season of the award-winning Netflix Original series “The Umbrella Academy” and in an upcoming ABC Studios comedy series “How to Die Alone”. https://lnkd.in/ghzMiqbK Thank you eBoss Canada, Hero Artists, Jessica Martins 💕 #actor #actorslife #filmmaker #losangeles #writer #producer
